Chandler, easy, easy. Go to your happy place. La la la la la la la.

222
00:19:14,543 --> 00:19:16,918
I'm fine./ OK. All right.

223
00:19:16,918 --> 00:19:20,830
I'm not fine. Here she comes./ Wait here. Breathe.

224
00:19:38,650 --> 00:19:40,170
How do you do that?

225
00:19:40,221 --> 00:19:41,781
It's like a gift.

226
00:19:44,338 --> 00:19:47,361
We should always always break up together.

227
00:19:47,361 --> 00:19:50,410
Oh, I'd like that.

228
00:19:50,410 --> 00:19:53,122
You got the clothes clean. Now that's the important part.

229
00:19:53,171 --> 00:19:57,742
Oh, I guess. Except everything looks like jammies now.

230
00:20:01,824 --> 00:20:07,284
Whoa, I'm sorry. Excuse me. We had this cart.

231
00:20:07,284 --> 00:20:12,398
Yeah, well, I had a 24-inch waist. You lose things. Now come on, get outta my way.

232
00:20:12,398 --> 00:20:15,941
I'm sorry, you know, maybe I wasn't being clear. Uh, this is our cart.

233
00:20:15,941 --> 00:20:17,934
Hey, hey, hey there aren't any clothes in it.

234
00:20:17,934 --> 00:20:20,492
Hey, hey, hey, hey, quit making up rules!

235
00:20:20,584 --> 00:20:23,343
Let go! !@#$%^

236
00:20:24,146 --> 00:20:28,729
All right, listen, missy. If you want this cart, you're gonna have to take me with it!

237
00:20:35,603 --> 00:20:38,508
Yes! Did you see that?

238
00:20:38,508 --> 00:20:41,100
You were incredible! Brand new woman, ladies and gentlemen.

239
00:20:41,199 --> 00:20:47,849
I could not have done this without you.

240
00:20:50,171 --> 00:20:58,217
Ok, um, uh, more clothes in the dryer? I'm fine, I'm fine.

241
00:21:02,356 --> 00:21:05,336
Oh, are you sure you're ok?/ Yeah.

242
00:21:05,336 --> 00:21:09,349
Does it still hurt?/ Yeah.

243
00:21:09,349 --> 00:21:14,570
What a neat idea. All your clothes match. I'm gonna do this.

244
00:21:14,570 --> 00:21:17,571
Hi./ Hey, how'd it go?

245
00:21:17,615 --> 00:21:18,538
Excellent.

246
00:21:18,573 --> 00:21:23,906
We ripped that couple apart, and kept the pieces for ourselves.

247
00:21:23,906 --> 00:21:28,245
What a beautiful story. Hey, I'm fine by the way.

248
00:21:28,245 --> 00:21:30,184
Oh, I'm sorry.

249
00:21:30,184 --> 00:21:31,795
Where's Chandler?

250
00:21:32,135 --> 00:21:33,511
Oh, he needed some time to grieve.

251
00:21:33,511 --> 00:21:37,695
I'm free! I'm free!

252
00:21:37,695 --> 00:21:39,461
That oughta do it.
